description: Dylan Ryan and Wenona team up against Izamar Gutierrez for the July Tag Team match up. Though both Dylan and Wenona haven't been on the mat for awhile they come back with a vengeance, and determination to win. Izamar has brute strength and training on her side, but the match comes to a close with a very close score. Stay tuned for next weeks tag team update to see who will pull further into the lead.
title: July Tag Team: Rd 1- 4 Sexy Wrestlers Battle for Dominance and Control
